title: 16 Bit Discography - All  Vinyl, Remixes, Mixes + In The Death C
description:
This is my 16 Bit Discography

16 Bit are a heavy Dubstep duo from the UK:

This discography contains all remixes he has done to date that are available (excluding a few exclusive remixes used in promo mixes), and all Vinyl released, including his digital EP.

Also contains many mixes including Electronic Explorations mix, Kissy Sell Out, Mary Anne Hobbs and Tokyo Set Menu Mix.

I have also included a Dub and Run vinyl that 16 Bit produced with dub and run wich is evident in the style.

For more info see rip info file contained.

All tunes 320k!

Enjoy
